latestPosts.caption:
Your smile is a spark that lights up everything, but it’s your eyes, delicate and full of quiet strength, that hold me captive, drawing me into the depths of you. The way they soften when you’re lost in thought, or dance with mischief when you laugh, it’s like I’m seeing something unguarded, a place you don’t let everyone in. Your curves, graceful and unassuming, feel like art brought to life, and the way you move speaks of a quiet confidence, a beauty that needs no announcement. 

Your hair falls so perfectly, framing your face, as if it knows it’s part of something rare.

But your heart, your heart is where the magic lives. It’s tender, yet fierce, it loves without holding back and cares with a depth that most wouldn’t understand. And your mind, so intricate and full of quiet wonders, captivates me in every conversation. It’s like each part of you, seen and unseen, has been crafted to perfection. To know you, to truly know you, is to understand what it means to be completely, irrevocably enchanted.

~ just, someone who adores beauty🌻

latestPosts.caption:
It is beautiful how time holds all the cards and you have no hold over it until you know your cards.
I find myself thinking about how ironic it is to lose time without even knowing I spent it. Honestly, that’s how life should be lived. 
There are days where I am struggling to take time out from chaotic work schedules to actually spend time of quiet. 
Life is pacing but time is consistently flowing and that is scary. 
Time is like a serpent and a dove at the same time. 
It is said, “Time is money”. Well, it surely is one of the most expensive pleasures of life.
~🌹
